Classic Accounting would be the source of truth for customers. Certain edits would need to be made in Classic Accounting, then would be transferred over into the software solution.

  


![](data:image/png;base64,)

  


The following fields will be migrated:

  * ID
  * Name (display name)
  * First Name
  * Middle Name
  * Last Name
  * Email
  * Phone (Blank type)
  * Alt. Phone (Blank type)
  * Fax (Fax type)
  * Bill To Address
  * Ship To Address
